text: Indy Baijens (born 4 February 2001 in Zaandam) is a Dutch volleyball player for ASPTT Mulhouse and the Dutch national team. She participated at the 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship and 2019 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. == References == == Other websites == *FIVB profile, *CEV profile Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Zaanstad
